# Allow-list for the link checker (regex, one per line).
# These URLs are valid in a browser but fail automated checks, so we skip them
# to avoid false-positive "broken link" reports. Keep this list small and
# documented; only add links that are confirmed reachable manually.

# raspberrypi.com returns HTTP 403 to non-browser clients (anti-bot).
^https://www\.raspberrypi\.com/

# star-history badge API is a dynamic image endpoint that intermittently 503s.
^https://api\.star-history\.com/

# mdpi.com (Cloudflare) returns HTTP 403 to non-browser clients (anti-bot).
^https://www\.mdpi\.com/
